  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Two tapping scripts for Day 8. The first works with a mind that keeps leaving the present during the day — jumping to tomorrow's plans or replaying what happened. The second is the bedtime version: a practice for arriving fully in the room before sleep."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "New to tapping? Read "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"}}],
            "text": "how EFT tapping works"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " first."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 1: Come back to now (daytime)"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though my mind keeps running ahead or rewinding, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I struggle to stay here in this moment, I honour how that habit once kept me safe."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though being present feels uncomfortable, I'm open to landing fully here and now."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My brain is always one step ahead."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I relive the past or worry about the future."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " But life only happens in this breath."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I want to feel the ground under my feet again."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can notice what's actually happening, not what might."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My safety lives in this moment."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can let go of everything outside now."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Here is enough."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm safe in the present."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can feel my breath anchoring me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can see, hear, and sense life right here."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " The past is done; the future can wait."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I choose this calm, current moment."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Presence feels peaceful."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can live today one grounded breath at a time."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I rest in the safety of now."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 2: Arrive in this moment before sleep"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though my mind keeps time-travelling, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I drift into what-ifs instead of rest, I honour my brain's habit of scanning for safety."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I've been everywhere but here, I'm open to returning to this quiet moment tonight."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm still thinking about tomorrow's plans."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I replay what I said today."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My mind moves fast, but my body is ready to stop."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can call all my energy back to this room."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can land in this bed, in this breath."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Nothing else exists right now."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " This moment is enough."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I arrive fully here."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm completely safe in this moment."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I let the day dissolve behind me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I don't need to reach ahead."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I rest between breaths, between thoughts."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Stillness feels real and solid."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " This moment holds all the peace I need."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I breathe, present and calm."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I fall asleep grounded in now."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times."}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 8 of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "italic"}],
            "text": "SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (Rebecca J Page, 2025). The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), developed in the mid-1990s."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
